	<entry>
		<title>비공개 repository npm으로 배포하기</title>
		<link href="https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/"/>
		<updated>2021-07-28T00:00:00Z</updated>
		<id>https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/</id>
		<content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD%2F%ED%98%B9%EC%9D%80-%EB%8D%94-%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%EC%9B%90%EB%B3%B8-%EA%B8%80&quot;&gt;요약/혹은 더 보기 좋은 원본 글 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD%2F%ED%98%B9%EC%9D%80-%EB%8D%94-%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80-%EC%9B%90%EB%B3%B8-%EA%B8%80&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/@changjoopark/%EC%82%AC%EB%82%B4-%EC%9C%A0%ED%8B%B8%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B0-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-npm-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-e1741614611b&quot;&gt;사내 유틸리티 메소드를 NPM 패키지로 관리하기&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;%EC%9E%AC%ED%98%84&quot;&gt;재현 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#%EC%9E%AC%ED%98%84&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;1.-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88-%EB%93%B1-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A0-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-git-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C%EB%A1%9C-%EB%94%B0%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B9%BC%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;1. 공통 모듈 등 관리할 모듈을 git 저장소로 따로 빼기 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#1.-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88-%EB%93%B1-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A0-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-git-%EC%A0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%86%8C%EB%A1%9C-%EB%94%B0%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B9%BC%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;2.-git-%EC%A3%BC%EC%86%8C-%EB%B0%9B%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;2. git 주소 받기 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#2.-git-%EC%A3%BC%EC%86%8C-%EB%B0%9B%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그냥 클론할 때 사용하는 주소 받으면 됨&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;3.-package.json%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC%2C-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8&quot;&gt;3. package.json에 정보 설정하여, 접근할 수 있는지 테스트 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#3.-package.json%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC%2C-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// package.json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;dependencies&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// ...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;[module-name]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;git+http://[id]:[password]@[git-url]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;4.-%EB%B9%84%EB%B0%80%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8-%EC%9E%85%EB%A0%A5-%EB%8C%80%EC%8B%A0-%ED%86%A0%ED%81%B0-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;4. 비밀번호 입력 대신 토큰 사용하기 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#4.-%EB%B9%84%EB%B0%80%EB%B2%88%ED%98%B8-%EC%9E%85%EB%A0%A5-%EB%8C%80%EC%8B%A0-%ED%86%A0%ED%81%B0-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;access-token-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;Access Token 만들기 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#access-token-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;bitbucket(v6.8.1)은 Manage Account &amp;gt; Personal access tokens&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;토큰명 지정하고 생성(권한은 읽기 권한만 있으면 될듯)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/img/2021-07-28-13-03-29.png&quot; alt=&quot;Tokens in bitbucket(v6.8.1)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;토큰 나오면 복사해두기&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;package.json에 password 대신 토큰 입력하기&lt;pre class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-js&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// package.json&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;dependencies&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;token comment&quot;&gt;// ...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;[module-name]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;git+http://[id]:[access-token]@[git-url]&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0&quot;&gt;참고 &lt;a class=&quot;direct-link&quot; href=&quot;https://saintkim12.github.io/techblog/posts/publish-private-npm/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.npmjs.com/files/package.json#git-urls-as-dependencies&quot;&gt;npm package.json 관련&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
